Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
**guid** | _uuid_ | Unique identifier for the revision.
**version** | _integer_ | Human-readable identifier for the revision. Starts at 1, increments by 1 for each new revision of the app, and rolls back over to 1 at 9999.
**droplet** | _object_ | The droplet used by a process running the revision.
**created_at** | _datetime_ | The time with zone when the object was created.
**updated_at** | _datetime_ | The time with zone when the object was last updated.
**description** | _string_ | A short description of the revision
**metadata.labels** _(experimental)_| [_label object_](#labels) | Labels applied to the revision.
**metadata.annotations** _(experimental)_ | [_annotation object_](#annotations) | Annotations applied to the revision.
**links** | [_links object_](#links) | Links to related resources.
